%% Diagram: Fan Out Parallelism
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
  T[Trigger: PR or push] --> L[Lint and format]
  T --> TC[Typecheck]
  T --> US1[Unit shard 1]
  T --> US2[Unit shard 2]
  T --> US3[Unit shard N]
  T --> SEC[Secret scan]
  T --> SCA[Dependency review]
  L --> J{All cheap checks pass?}
  TC --> J
  US1 --> J
  US2 --> J
  US3 --> J
  SEC --> J
  SCA --> J
  J -->|No| X[Block merge or queue]
  J -->|Yes| B[Build once: image addressed by digest]
  B --> I1[Integration: service A]
  B --> I2[Integration: service B]
  B --> SAST[SAST on artifact]
  B --> ATT[Provenance and SBOM]
  I1 --> P[Promote candidate to staging]
  I2 --> P
  SAST --> P
  ATT --> P
